{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7dfb6152d0","title":"在关于英国各界对我撤销出口合同的反应报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fa5ff5a985","index":0,"year":1959,"month":2,"day":19,"articleId":"7dfb6152d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"b93152c970","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国驻英国代办处商务参赞1959年2月14日给外贸部并外交部的这一报告说，上海土产公司与英商成交霜黄棉约2000吨，最近该公司以政府不发许可证为由撤销合同，此事已引起英国各界广泛注意和评论。我代办处在对外接触时，对类似上述问题一般不明确说明原因，亦不强调运输问题，有时适当指出贸易发展必须以政治友好为前提，对有些客户，尽量说服其接受撤销部分合约。我们认为，今后如毁约面太广，将对我政治上造成不利影响，故建议国内各公司应尽量缩小不履约的品种和客户范围，确实无法交货，亦应与对方协商解决，置之不理态度，将更会造成对方的对立情绪，采取不利于我的行动。"},{"id":"edd90e8a1a","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9e3f1cfe98","type":"title","text":"在关于英国各界对我撤销出口合同的反应报告“上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0"},{"id":"b93152c970","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来、陈毅同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0"},{"id":"edd90e8a1a","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么采取这种政策，是否有利，请查明告我为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0"},{"id":"ffe76ecaf1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0"},{"id":"4cd65cfc10","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0"}],"page":{"id":"a1b2e77034","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"7dfb6152d0","start":226,"end":226}}}},"__N_SSG":true}